### Closira API — HTTP Test File
### Works with REST Client (VS Code extension) or IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### ── 1. Health Check ────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### ── 2. Create Enquiry — Pricing Question ───────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Sarah M",
  "message": "I want pricing details for your service"
}

###

### ── 3. Create Enquiry — Booking ────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "email",
  "customer_name": "James K",
  "message": "I'd like to book an appointment for next Tuesday"
}

###

### ── 4. Create Enquiry — Complaint ─────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "call",
  "customer_name": "Priya S",
  "message": "I have a complaint about the service — this is terrible and I am very upset"
}

###

### ── 5. Create Enquiry — Demo Request ──────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Marcus T",
  "message": "Can you show me a demo of your product? I'd love a walkthrough"
}

###

### ── 6. Create Enquiry — No SOP match (triggers auto-escalation)

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "email",
  "customer_name": "Unknown User",
  "message": "xyzzy frobozz magic zork nonsense string"
}

###

### ── 7. Schedule Follow-up (replace {id} with actual enquiry ID)

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/REPLACE_WITH_ENQUIRY_ID/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 30,
  "message_template": "Following up regarding your enquiry. We'd love to help!"
}

###

### ── 8. Escalate Enquiry (replace {id} with actual enquiry ID)

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/REPLACE_WITH_ENQUIRY_ID/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer requested to speak with a manager"
}

###

### ── 9. Get Enquiry History (replace {id} with actual enquiry ID)

GET {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/REPLACE_WITH_ENQUIRY_ID/history
Accept: application/json

###

### ── 10. Invalid channel (should return 422) ───────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "telegram",
  "customer_name": "Test User",
  "message": "Hello"
}

###

### ── 11. Follow-up on escalated enquiry (should return 422) ────

POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/REPLACE_WITH_ESCALATED_ID/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 15
}

###
